name.jp: スノーフェアリーの翼

description.en: I believe in everything until it's disproved. So I believe in fairies, the myths, dragons. It all exists, even if it's in your mind.
description.ar: I believe in everything until it's disproved. So I believe in fairies, the myths, dragons. It all exists, even if it's in your mind.
description.br: Eu acredito em tudo até que seja refutado. Então eu acredito em fadas, em mitos, em dragões. Tudo existe, mesmo que só em nossas mentes.
description.cns: 我相信一切，直到它被证伪。 所以我相信仙女，神话，龙。 这一切都存在，即使它只在你的脑海中。
description.fi: I believe in everything until it's disproved. So I believe in fairies, the myths, dragons. It all exists, even if it's in your mind.
description.fil: I believe in everything until it's disproved. So I believe in fairies, the myths, dragons. It all exists, even if it's in your mind.
description.id: Aku mempercayai segalanya sampai itu dibantah. Aku percaya peri, mitos, naga. Itu semua ada meskipun hanya dalam imajinasi.
description.it: I believe in everything until it's disproved. So I believe in fairies, the myths, dragons. It all exists, even if it's in your mind.
description.jp: 妖精やドラゴンがたとえ神話であっても、心の中で信じていれば存在し、生きているという証明になるのです。
description.kr: 나는 그것이 반증 될 때까지 모든 것을 믿습니다. 그래서 저는 요정, 신화, 용을 믿습니다. 그것은 당신의 마음에 있더라도 모두 존재합니다.
description.nl: I believe in everything until it's disproved. So I believe in fairies, the myths, dragons. It all exists, even if it's in your mind.
description.pl: I believe in everything until it's disproved. So I believe in fairies, the myths, dragons. It all exists, even if it's in your mind.
description.ru: I believe in everything until it's disproved. So I believe in fairies, the myths, dragons. It all exists, even if it's in your mind.
description.sp: Creo en todo hasta que se refuta. Así que creo en las hadas, los mitos, los dragones. Todo existe, incluso si está en tu mente.
description.sw: I believe in everything until it's disproved. So I believe in fairies, the myths, dragons. It all exists, even if it's in your mind.
description.th: ฉันเชื่อในทุกสิ่งจนถูกหักล้าง ฉันจึงเชื่อในนางฟ้า เทพนิยาย มังกร มีอยู่ทั้งหมดแม้ว่าจะอยู่ในใจของคุณ
description.tw: 我相信一切，直到它被證偽。 所以我相信仙女，神話，龍，這一切都存在，即使它只在你的腦海中。
description.vi: Tôi tin vào mọi thứ cho đến khi nó bị bác bỏ. Vì vậy, tôi tin vào thần tiên, thần thoại, rồng. Tất cả đều tồn tại, ngay cả khi nó ở trong tâm trí bạn.
